# RAG Chatbot Project - Trump Persona (Educational)

This project creates a customizable RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) chatbot for educational purposes.

## Project Overview
- **Purpose**: Educational RAG chatbot that students can customize with different personas
- **Default Persona**: Donald Trump (example - easily changeable)
- **Platform**: Google Colab (free tier)
- **Technologies**: ChromaDB, Google Gemini API, Gradio, Sentence Transformers
- **Cost**: 100% free - no subscriptions or paywalls

## Current Status
✅ Initial notebook created: `RAG_Chatbot_Trump_Persona.ipynb`
- Complete end-to-end RAG implementation
- Gradio chat interface
- Simple text fallback interface
- Comprehensive documentation
- Student-friendly with detailed comments
- Easy persona customization

## Key Features
1. PDF document processing from Google Drive
2. Vector database with ChromaDB
3. Semantic search using embeddings
4. Persona-based responses via Google Gemini
5. Dual interface options (Gradio UI + simple text)
6. Adjustable response parameters (temperature, style, etc.)

## Student Workflow
1. Upload notebook to Google Colab
2. Get free Google Gemini API key
3. Upload PDFs to Google Drive
4. Configure persona settings (Block 4)
5. Run all cells sequentially
6. Chat with personalized bot

## Next Steps (Planned)
- Additional features to be added per user request
- Keep everything free and beginner-friendly
- Maintain single-notebook structure

## Technical Architecture
```
PDFs → Text Extraction → Chunking → Embeddings → ChromaDB
                                                      ↓
User Question → Query Embedding → Similarity Search → Context
                                                      ↓
                                    Context + Persona → Gemini API → Response
```

